Package: plexinstaller
Version: __VERSION__
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-venv, python3-pip, curl, git, jq, gnupg, nodejs (>= 20), npm
Maintainer: Bali0531-RC <contact@bali0531.hu>
Homepage: https://github.com/Bali0531-RC/plexinstaller
Description: Unified installer for PlexDevelopment bots and Drako products
 PlexInstaller is the unified Python-based installer and management
 tool for PlexTickets, PlexStaff, and Drako Status, Store, Forms, Links,
 Paste, and Tracker. It handles archive discovery,
 extraction, dependency installation, MongoDB/user provisioning,
 nginx + SSL wiring, firewall rules, telemetry, and post-install
 management from a single interactive CLI workflow.
